What's wrong with cloning here?

Sure. If you have `fn parse_number(s: &str) -> Result<u64, _> { Some(serde_json::from_str::<u64>(s).unwrap()) }` it forces panic on invalid input; a safer pattern would be `match parse_number(s) {
    Ok(v) => v,
    Err(e) => return Err(e),
}`. unwrap here is unnecessary and hides errors.
